---
import DocsLayout from '@layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout>
  <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/docs">Docs</a>
    <span class="breadcrumbs__sep">›</span>
    <span>Introduction</span>
  </nav>

  <h1 class="docs-page-title">Introduction</h1>
  <p class="docs-page-lead">
    Bitcoin API gives you fast, reliable access to Bitcoin market data through a simple REST API and real-time WebSocket
    streams. Built for developers and vibe coders who want to ship quickly without running their own infrastructure.
  </p>

  <h2 id="what-you-can-do">What you can do</h2>
  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card__icon">
        <svg
          width="20"
          height="20"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          ><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline></svg
        >
      </div>
      <h3>Real-time Market Data</h3>
      <p>Stream live prices, trades, and order book updates from major exchanges as they happen.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card__icon">
        <svg
          width="20"
          height="20"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg
        >
      </div>
      <h3>Historical Market Data</h3>
      <p>Query OHLCV candles and trade history across exchanges for backtesting and analysis.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card__icon">
        <svg
          width="20"
          height="20"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          ><path d="M4 4h6v6H4z"></path><path d="M14 4h6v6h-6z"></path><path d="M4 14h6v6H4z"></path><path
            d="M14 14h6v6h-6z"></path></svg
        >
      </div>
      <h3>Real-time On-chain Data</h3>
      <p>Track new blocks, mempool activity, and address events on the Bitcoin network as they confirm.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-card__icon">
        <svg
          width="20"
          height="20"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          ><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5v14a9 3 0 0 0 18 0V5"></path><path
            d="M3 12a9 3 0 0 0 18 0"></path></svg
        >
      </div>
      <h3>Historical On-chain Data</h3>
      <p>Look up past blocks, transactions, and address balances across the full Bitcoin chain history.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="built-for">Built for everyone shipping with Bitcoin data</h2>
  <p class="docs-page-text">
    Our goal is simple: be the most comfortable Bitcoin API for developers, vibe coders, and AI agents. Each audience
    gets tools tailored to how they actually work.
  </p>

  <div class="audience-list">
    <div class="audience-card">
      <div class="audience-card__header">
        <div class="audience-card__icon">
          <svg
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3>For developers</h3>
      </div>
      <p>Powerful search with an AI assistant that knows the entire API surface, so you find the right endpoint fast.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="audience-card">
      <div class="audience-card__header">
        <div class="audience-card__icon">
          <svg
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3>For vibe coders</h3>
      </div>
      <p>MCP tools and N8N integrations so you can wire Bitcoin data into your stack without writing glue code.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="audience-card">
      <div class="audience-card__header">
        <div class="audience-card__icon">
          <svg
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"></rect><circle cx="8.5" cy="10" r="1.5"></circle><circle
              cx="15.5"
              cy="10"
              r="1.5"></circle><path d="M8 15h8"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <h3>For AI agents</h3>
      </div>
      <p>MCP tools and static HTML documentation that's easy to crawl, parse, and reason about.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
  .breadcrumbs {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .breadcrumbs a {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .breadcrumbs a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .breadcrumbs__sep {
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .docs-page-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .docs-page-lead {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .docs-page-text {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  /* ── Feature grid ── */

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .feature-card__icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: #eff6ff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.375rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Audience cards ── */

  .audience-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .audience-card {
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .audience-card__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .audience-card__icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: #eff6ff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .audience-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .audience-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
